            <!-- /Our Team -->\n\n        <!-- Testimonials -->\n                <!-- /Testimonials -->\n\n        <!-- About event -->\n                    <section class="page-section about-event">\n                  <div class="region region-about-event">\n    \n\n<section id="block-block-2" class="block block-block clearfix">\n\n    <div class="container">\n                                <p><em><strong>INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM OF HUMAN’S HEALTH AND AGING SCIENCES (ISHHAS)</strong></em></p>\n<p>For the 2nd ISHHAS, we would like to discuss about several updates about endocrine especially with elderly problems. <strong>The 2nd ISHHAS will be collaborating with Indonesian Endocrinology Association</strong>. The output for ISHHAS will be for the publication purposes for international researchers. Furthermore, to extend the market for the targeted audience the preparation for sub themes and speakers appointment who will participate in this event, we would like to organize a pre conference meeting by inviting the Steering Committee from 4 countries which are\xa0<strong>Indonesia, Malaysia, Netherland and Jordania</strong>,\xa0and also representatives from\xa0<strong>Indonesian Endocrinology Association</strong>\xa0in order to prepare <strong>the\xa02<sup>nd</sup>\xa0ISHHAS.</strong></p>\n<p>\xa0</p>\n<p><em><strong>SUB TOPICS:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>1.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Thyroid\xa0<br />\n2.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Reproductive Disorder<br />\n3. \xa0 \xa0 Diabetes Mellitus Type 1 &amp; 2<br />\n4.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Breast Cancer<br />\n5.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Cardiovasculer</strong></em><br />\n\xa0</p>\n<p><em><strong>Travel Grants are provided for limited participants.<br />\nTerms &amp; conditions apply.\xa0<br />\nFor further information please contact secretariat.</strong></em></p>\n<p>\xa0</p>\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT DATES:</strong></p>\n<p><em>- Abstract submission for oral or poster presentation: Desember \xa015th, 2016<br />\n-\xa0Notification of acceptance: December 15th, 2016\xa0<br />\n- Deadline registration: December 30th, 2016</em></p>\n<p><strong>PAPER PUBLICATION:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>*) Abstract max. 250 words</em></strong><br /><strong><em>*) Full Paper 8-10 pages in English<br />\n*)\xa0Presentation language: English<br />\n*) Publication: Ishhas Proceeding ISBN, SCOPUS Indexed, Bangladesh Journal Of medical Sciences, Range of Issue 2017 - 2018</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>PAYMENT:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>Bank Transfer / Western Union:<br />\nBank Negara Indonesia (BNI Indonesia)<br />\nAccount No. 371569881\xa0<br />\nc/o Ulfah Dian Indrayani<br />\n* Exclude accommodation / transportation to venue\xa0</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>FOR FURTHER INFORMATION:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Secretariat: Faculty of Medicine, Sultan Agung \xa0Islamic University\xa0<br />\nKaligawe KM 4, Semarang-Central Java-Indonesia<br />\nEmail : <a href="mailto:ishhas@unissula.ac.id">ishhas@unissula.ac.id</a><br            <div class="region region-content">\n    \n\n<section id="block-system-main" class="block block-system clearfix">\n\n            \n        <div id="node-60" class="node node-article             <!-- /Our Team -->\n\n        <!-- Testimonials -->\n                <!-- /Testimonials -->\n\n        <!-- About event -->\n                    <section class="page-section about-event">\n                  <div class="region region-about-event">\n    \n\n<section id="block-block-2" class="block block-block clearfix">\n\n    <div class="container">\n                                <p><em><strong>INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM OF HUMAN’S HEALTH AND AGING SCIENCES (ISHHAS)</strong></em></p>\n<p>For the 2nd ISHHAS, we would like to discuss about several updates about endocrine especially with elderly problems. <strong>The 2nd ISHHAS will be collaborating with Indonesian Endocrinology Association</strong>. The output for ISHHAS will be for the publication purposes for international researchers. Furthermore, to extend the market for the targeted audience the preparation for sub themes and speakers appointment who will participate in this event, we would like to organize a pre conference meeting by inviting the Steering Committee from 4 countries which are\xa0<strong>Indonesia, Malaysia, Netherland and Jordania</strong>,\xa0and also representatives from\xa0<strong>Indonesian Endocrinology Association</strong>\xa0in order to prepare <strong>the\xa02<sup>nd</sup>\xa0ISHHAS.</strong></p>\n<p>\xa0</p>\n<p><em><strong>SUB TOPICS:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>1.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Thyroid\xa0<br />\n2.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Reproductive Disorder<br />\n3. \xa0 \xa0 Diabetes Mellitus Type 1 &amp; 2<br />\n4.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Breast Cancer<br />\n5.\xa0\xa0 \xa0 Cardiovasculer</strong></em><br />\n\xa0</p>\n<p><em><strong>Travel Grants are provided for limited participants.<br />\nTerms &amp; conditions apply.\xa0<br />\nFor further information please contact secretariat.</strong></em></p>\n<p>\xa0</p>\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT DATES:</strong></p>\n<p><em>- Abstract submission for oral or poster presentation: Desember \xa015th, 2016<br />\n-\xa0Notification of acceptance: December 15th, 2016\xa0<br />\n- Deadline registration: December 30th, 2016</em></p>\n<p><strong>PAPER PUBLICATION:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>*) Abstract max. 250 words</em></strong><br /><strong><em>*) Full Paper 8-10 pages in English<br />\n*)\xa0Presentation language: English<br />\n*) Publication: Ishhas Proceeding ISBN, SCOPUS Indexed, Bangladesh Journal Of medical Sciences, Range of Issue 2017 - 2018</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>PAYMENT:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>Bank Transfer / Western Union:<br />\nBank Negara Indonesia (BNI Indonesia)<br />\nAccount No. 371569881\xa0<br />\nc/o Ulfah Dian Indrayani<br />\n* Exclude accommodation / transportation to venue\xa0</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>FOR FURTHER INFORMATION:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Secretariat: Faculty of Medicine, Sultan Agung \xa0Islamic University\xa0<br />\nKaligawe KM 4, Semarang-Central Java-Indonesia<br />\nEmail : <a href="mailto:ishhas@unissula.ac.id">ishhas@unissula.ac.id</a><br />\nPhone : (+62 24) 658 3584 ext. 550, Fax : (+62 24) 658 2455<br />\nCP: +62 815-7725-620 (Nurul), +62 815-7752-883 (Dina),<br />\n+62 858-7689-4656 (Putri)<br />\nWebsite : <a href="http://ishhas.fkunissula.ac.id/">http://ishhas.fkunissula.ac.id/</a></strong></p>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-6">\n<p class="btn-theme-group"><a class="btn btn-theme btn-theme-primary" href="http://ishhas.fkunissula.ac.id/registrasi/">Register\xa0</a></p>\n<hr class="page-divider half hidden-md" /></div>\n<div class="col-md-12">\n<div class="row">\n<div
